# MVVM Architecture Pattern

The app follows the Model-View-ViewModel (MVVM) pattern:

## Models
Located in [BibleReader/Models/](mdc:BibleReader/Models/):
- [BibleContent.swift](mdc:BibleReader/Models/BibleContent.swift) - Core Bible content data structures
- [BibleMetadata.swift](mdc:BibleReader/Models/BibleMetadata.swift) - Bible metadata and configuration
- [Bookmark.swift](mdc:BibleReader/Models/Bookmark.swift) - User bookmark data model

## Views
Located in [BibleReader/Views/](mdc:BibleReader/Views/):
- [ContentView.swift](mdc:BibleReader/Views/ContentView.swift) - Main navigation and layout
- [VerseViews.swift](mdc:BibleReader/Views/VerseViews.swift) - Bible verse display components
- [SearchView.swift](mdc:BibleReader/Views/SearchView.swift) - Search interface
- [BookmarkViews.swift](mdc:BibleReader/Views/BookmarkViews.swift) - Bookmark management UI

## ViewModels
Located in [BibleReader/ViewModels/](mdc:BibleReader/ViewModels/):
- [BibleViewModel.swift](mdc:BibleReader/ViewModels/BibleViewModel.swift) - Main Bible content management
- [SearchViewModel.swift](mdc:BibleReader/ViewModels/SearchViewModel.swift) - Search functionality
- [BookmarkStore.swift](mdc:BibleReader/ViewModels/BookmarkStore.swift) - Bookmark persistence
